body:
# geonames-for-postgis
====================

This utility is for building the [GeoNames](http://www.geonames.org/) database in PostGIS v. 2 in an automated fashion. 

Assumptions:
PostgreSQL v. 9.+
PostGIS v. 2.+
name: Geonames-for-postgis
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
tagline: This utility is for building the geonames database in PostGIS v. 2 in an automated fashion.
